    "In April 2021, SNC spun off its space capabilities into a new commercial space company, Sierra Space.",
    "Sierra Space, which raised $290 million at a $5.3 billion valuation in September 2023, is set to launch its first flight of a cargo spaceplane called Dream Chaser in 2025.",
    "Ozmen and her husband Fatih, both Turkish immigrants, bought SNC in 1994 when it had just 20 employees."
